The Winter Soldiers

FTC Team #8813

About Us

We are an eighth year FIRST Tech Challenge team consisting of 15 students from Bettendorf, Iowa and the surrounding area. We are committed to creating competitive, industrially designed robots and spreading our passion for robotics across the globe. Over the past few years, we've worked to promote STEM in Iowa, Illinois, Alaska, Solomon Islands, Micronesia, Somalia, North Macedonia, Burundi, Russia, and India.
